Text:
Hello smd, I'm amazed at your collection of Beatles music, I'm not much into them, so am passing on these torrents.

Some time ago, you commented that funds were tight for you.  

On this site, have a look at user DOOLY-WZMB. I was browsing a moment or two ago and found this person's collection.  I can't attest as to the quality or reliability of the torrents, just posting this info to help out.

Plenty of Grateful Dead, Jerry Garcia Band, Further, etc.  Many sound boards.
